| Access to Essentials     | Proximity to shops, healthcare, public services      | Convenience, health access                     | The Top Qualities That Define A Good Neighborhood (2020) |
| Walkability              | Infrastructure for walking/biking                     | Physical activity, social interaction         | Healthy People 2030; PPS (2008)             |
| Green Spaces & Aesthetics| Trees, parks, clean streets                            | Environmental health, community pride         | PPS (2008); The Top Qualities (2020)        |
| Housing Variety          | Diverse housing types                                 | Inclusivity, lifecycle accommodation          | The Top Qualities (2020)                     |
| Social Cohesion          | Sense of belonging, community engagement              | Mental health, economic growth                 | McMillan & Chavis (1986); Knight Foundation (2010) |
| Economic Stability       | Affordable housing, job opportunities                  | Resident retention, quality of life            | Niche (2025)                                |
| Education Quality        | Good schools                                         | Family attraction, property values             | Trulia (2025)                               |
| Environmental Health     | Clean air/water, low pollution                        | Long-term health outcomes                       | Healthy People 2030                          |

